# MongoDB

## Access

- Driver imported only in `main/database/` and `main/repositories/`
- Single shared connection from `connection.ts` — reuse pool, handle reconnect

## Repositories

- Extend or compose `base.repository.ts` for common CRUD
- Collection names: plural snake_case (`orders`, `customer_ledger`)
- Return typed documents; map `_id` to string DTOs for IPC when needed

## Migrations

- Track `app_meta.schemaVersion`
- Migrations in `main/database/migrations/` run on startup before IPC serves requests

## Indexes

- Define in `index-manager.ts` grouped by phase — see `docs/DATABASE.md`

## Snapshots

- Orders store product name/price/tax snapshots — do not join live product price for historical bills
